| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3030 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aaa8ae4a-32e5-5251-ae7f-ac0dcb34940b"
